\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Stellenbosch University is a public higher education institution with programmes that are accredited by the CHE.\line \line The Institution is currently applying for accreditation of a Postgraduate Diploma in Accounting programme which will be offered in the contact mode of delivery at the Stellenbosch\'2C Main Campus.\line \line The Institution has the following programmes that are HEQSF-Aligned and deemed Accredited\'3A\line - Bachelor of Accounting \line - Bachelor of Accounting Honours \line - Bachelor of Commerce in Management Accounting \line - Bachelor of Commerce Honours in Financial Accounting \line - Bachelor of Commerce Honours in Management Accounting \line - Master of Accounting \line - Master of Accounting in Auditing \line - Master of Accounting in Financial Accounting \line - Master of Accounting in Taxation \line - Master of Commerce in Management Accounting \line - Doctor of Philosophy in Accounting \line - Doctor of Philosophy in Financial Accounting \line - Doctor of Philosophy in Management Accounting \cell \pard 

